stent\noscillations are suppressed, and thermalisation time decreases. The general\nthermalisation pattern is globally top-down, but a closer look reveals\ncomplexities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2016 19:51:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2016 15:28:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2016 08:52:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-15"}
