ate the common\nfactors than directly used for forecasts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2016 01:38:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2018 02:54:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-18"}
